1674c6dc1a1a568a","tid":2363281,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"問題係如果美國唔罩住台灣<br />\n日台聯防夠唔夠抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"冇美國，即使日+台+韓都唔會夠支那打，如果加埋南海諸國嚟個十國聯軍應該可以打敗支那"},{"pid":"4f202cecb80a38cddcb19dbcc3506ad3924395f9","tid":2363281,"uid":126382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"934300d1103701a13d52c4f31674c6dc1a1a568a","tid":2363281,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"問題係如果美國唔罩住台灣<br />\n日台聯防夠唔夠抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"依家開打嘅話夠<br />\n<br />\n日本海軍係世界第二先進<br />\n<br />\n台灣海軍訓練充足，兩軍合作係好可怕，中共心知肚明"},{"pid":"07fd682a266872befd7a27fc9a2bae0cf8219831","tid":2363281,"uid":2654,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"日本人依家咁有錢有地位，得鬼閑同你擴張咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個國家如果有錢有地位淨返嘅就係如何守住自己地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講得出日本軍國主義再起嘅人，只係因為貧窮限制佢想象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0814bfb18ea9c64015003c2f37b57b94aea822","tid":2363281,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"仲有南韓呢？"},{"pid":"7e317273d84e79aefdfbec344f2b1c42bcd7254d","tid":2363281,"uid":2654,"like":7,"dislike":