義再起嘅人，只係因為貧窮限制佢想象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"依家係唔守連生存都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n島國依賴貿易換資源 <br />\n日本農業自給率係發達國家中好低<br />\n能源有限要買<br />\n仲有礦物、炭...<br />\n<br />\n海權國家失航道控制權死路一條<br />\n中國有方向係玩埋冰上一帶一路 暖化令到北冰洋航線有機會大搞<br />\n中國海運至北冰洋點都要經過北海道 所以支那做定部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本唔再解禁真係變日本省"},{"pid":"4bf323efada952bf06c3dcdb81cfd4ba4b16744c","tid":2363281,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e317273d84e79aefdfbec344f2b1c42bcd7254d","tid":2363281,"uid":2654,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"934300d1103701a13d52c4f31674c6dc1a1a568a","tid":2363281,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"問題係如果美國唔罩住台灣<br />\n日台聯防夠唔夠抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"海上艦隊決戰<br />\n<br />\n海自殲滅老解只係時間問題<br />\n<br />\n但要如何結束戰爭先係問題<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個問題老美都應該冇認真諗過<br />\n<br />\n即係台海戰爭若美國介入，美軍應該打到邊先叫結束"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"日本艦載機得f-35 打哂就玩撚完<br />\n支那機點廢都好都叫自給自足有自主供應鏈無限出<br />\n你可來得出海自殲滅到老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海自唯一比得上嘅得反潛能力<br />\n<br />\n台海一打 條海峽即變禁航區<br />\n所有美軍艦隻冇可能入去 一入即比反艦彈放題<br />\n仲有台灣以東五百里內都係支那東風飛彈範圍<br />\n航母一入去九成被打沉<br />\n唯一可能係關島用空中支援台灣<br />\n但幫極有限"},{"pid":"c921589a50ea0252d8930882a46dabbd9308ee98","tid":2363281,"uid":34804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ddbc54e1853b99deca9cf28382b5deac061235e0","tid":2363281,"uid":79562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07fd682a266872befd7a27fc9a2bae0cf8219831","tid":2363281,"uid":2654,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"日本人依家咁有錢有地位，得鬼閑同你擴張咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個國家如果有錢有地位淨返嘅就係如何守住自己地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講得出日本軍國主義再起嘅人，只係因為貧窮限制佢想象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"依家係唔守連生存都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n島國依賴貿易換資源 <br />\n日本農業自給率係發達國家中好低<br />\n能源有限要買<br />\n仲有礦物、炭...<br />\n<br />\n海權國家失航道控制權死路一條<br />\n中國有方向係玩埋冰上一帶一路 暖化令到北冰洋航線有機會大搞<br />\n中國海運至北冰洋點都要經過北海道 所以支那做定部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本唔再解禁真係變日本省"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"日本幾高科技都好，比中共控制住海路<br />\n無原材料無石油等收皮<br />\n同之前韓國無左日本加工品食哂屎咁一樣<br />\n<br />\n中共一心想做東亞霸權，日本得兩條路行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb70188429a03e4b2319bd0a26cd29fda4fa11a","tid":2363281,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.insider.com/5a8a52fad0307226028b463f?width=1200&amp;format=jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a8a52fad0307226028b463f%3Fwidth%3D1200%26format%3Djpeg&h=9ded86f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resources.stuff.co.nz/content/dam/images/4/y/p/h/z/j/image.related.StuffLandscapeSixteenByNine.710x400.21il71.png/1606199076916.jpg?format=pjpg&amp;optimize=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresources.stuff.co.nz%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fimage